scene.message:
Maki: So this is the{nl}
police station...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Right, right, I remember{nl}
this place!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:16}...{wait_fr:16}Right.{wait_fr:32}{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, Inaba should be{nl}
in the holding cell.{waitkey}{nl}
But we need a key to get{nl}
into the cell block.{nl}
What do we do...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Maybe it's{nl}
somewhere around here.{nl}
Let's look!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That makes sense.{nl}
{ctl0f:1},{nl}
help us search.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Inaba should be{nl}
in the cells.{waitkey}Not that I want to{nl}
rescue him, but he has{nl}
the "Security Card."{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: "Holding cell"...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Oh, the holding cell!{nl}
Yeah, yeah, that's a thing!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Hey, {ctl07:1},{nl}
Nanjo says I'm acting{nl}
weird — what do you think?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: {ctl08:65281}You think I was{nl}
in trouble and came{nl}
to rescue me?{waitkey}Tch! That's not it!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'd just thought of{nl}
a super-cool escape plan —{nl}
what a waste! Dang!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Once we had the card,{nl}
we could have just left{nl}
Inaba and Brown here.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: That old bastard!{nl}
How could you hand the cops{nl}
over to demons?!{waitkey}{clearbox}That old bastard...{nl}
I mean, the Inspector.{nl}
He'd collar me sometimes{nl}
and I'd get ticked,{waitkey}{clearbox}but he actually{nl}
gave a damn about me.{nl}
Don't tell me that{nl}
demon got to him...{waitkey}{clearbox}...Nah.{nl}
That overkill Inspector{nl}
wouldn't fall that easy.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: We need a key{nl}
to get into the cells.{nl}
Let's find it first.{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's search inside.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: They wouldn't leave{nl}
the key outside.{nl}
Search inside more.{waitkey}{clearbox}Keep looking.{waitkey}{ret}
